  br
  br
  | • You can change or cancel your contribution at any time before the request is accepted. Once the request has been accepted, you can only cancel or change your contribution by making special arrangements directly with the recipient.
  br
  br
  | • Any delivery date the recipient provides for when the request will be completed is an estimate — there is no guarantee the request will be fulfilled by that date. The schedule may change as the recipient works on the request. We ask recipients to think carefully, set a date they feel confident they can work toward, and communicate with backers about any changes.
  br
  br
